  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But you couldn't argue with your parents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They knew best.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] but and of course, that was the reason why she perished along with, with them because it was much too late.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I don't think she ever took her Abitur.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it was unthinkable for a bourgeois family to, to stop their daughter-- stop their-- for that bourgeois family, anyway.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were trying very hard at the same time, even though it was late in the day-- better late than never-- and they tried very hard to-- for themselves also, and, and my sister, to get out right until the end, until war broke out, even, even afterwards while America was still neutral.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and of course, no one-- I dare say no one at that time had an inkling of what the Holocaust would really consists of, what it would cover, and what it would-- what it would be.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, this was something that was unknown in the annals of civilization.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That, that, that, I dare say, I have yet, so many years after the war, to find anybody that says, I knew or he knew or they knew, or to show me where it was written, or who said that, that-- who could predict this.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This just wasn't-- so our-- I'm saying this in order to, to, to somehow convey that this was not unwarranted optimism to really think that there would be-- that we would be reunited, that this would be a temporary, rather than a permanent, separation.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's, that's the way that, that, that the whole thing was approached.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How much of this was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] kind of-- I can't answer for my parents.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I can't answer for my sister.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
